  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566450/extras/05582f6ae7f59e76f46c05e557a42f1c.avif?t=1730116047\" width=600 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game is made from a collection of stories from Yakutia about encounters with supernatural phenomena: ghosts, spirits. The terrible stories of Yakutia have their own flavor and connection with the folklore of the peoples of Yakutia.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In the first part of the game, you will find yourself within the walls of a school, where you will not only be tasked with fulfilling your duties but also unraveling mysteries. Under the director's guidance, you will need to solve a series of challenges that will reveal the hidden secrets of this educational establishment.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>The average playtime of the game is 1 hour and 30 minutes.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D SOUND (Headphones required)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Photo-realistic graphics;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voiceover in the Yakut language;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-quality sound support completely immerses in the game;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An exciting plot twist;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eerie and forcing atmosphere;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A scary story that will remain in your memory for a long time.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566450/extras/05582f6ae7f59e76f46c05e557a42f1c.avif?t=1730116047\" width=600 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game is made from a collection of stories from Yakutia about encounters with supernatural phenomena: ghosts, spirits. The terrible stories of Yakutia have their own flavor and connection with the folklore of the peoples of Yakutia.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In the first part of the game, you will find yourself within the walls of a school, where you will not only be tasked with fulfilling your duties but also unraveling mysteries. Under the director's guidance, you will need to solve a series of challenges that will reveal the hidden secrets of this educational establishment.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>The average playtime of the game is 1 hour and 30 minutes.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D SOUND (Headphones required)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Photo-realistic graphics;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voiceover in the Yakut language;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-quality sound support completely immerses in the game;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An exciting plot twist;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eerie and forcing atmosphere;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A scary story that will remain in your memory for a long time.</p></li></ul>",
